title: DDFP 368: 'Top 100' discussion & updated division winners
itunes:title: DDFP 368: 'Top 100' discussion & updated division winners
description:
Shek is joined by Elliot Harrison to discuss the final ‘Top 100 players’ rankings (29:14) and share if they agree with who grabbed the No.1 spot. The guys also discuss what teams need to do to win their respective division (36:40) and then revisit the best movie action star of all time (53:58).
